title: Surfside Tiara wins Anoakia Stakes at Santa Anita
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Surfside Tiara rallied in the final furlong to win the $70,000 Anoakia Stakes for 2-year-old fillies by a half-length Sunday at Santa Anita....
